<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .email-container {
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .email-content {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #2c3e50;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background-color: #3498db;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #ecf0f1;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #7f8c8d;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="email-content">
        <h1>Welcome to GMW API, <%= @template_data[:name] %>!</h1>
        <p>Thank you for joining our platform. We're excited to have you on board.</p>
        <p>Your account has been successfully created and you can now start using our services.</p>
        <% if @template_data[:activation_url].present? %>
          <a href="<%= @template_data[:activation_url] %>" class="button">Activate Your Account</a>
        <% end %>
        <div class="footer">
          <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

